# {{pejorative|slang}} A derisive term for a [[lowlife]] or a [[slob]] (could be treated as plural or singular).

=====Usage notes=====
* This is the plural form of the word.  While it is often used as if it were singular (as a collective noun), this is considered nonstandard by some in the US and more elsewhere.  See the usage examples under {{term|bacterium}}.

